abstract: >-
  Wave A.2 implementation of the qByte substrate-engineering suite featuring
  phase-conjugate acoustic coupling, quaternion-tetrahedral torsion mechanics,
  51.843° dielectric lock, ΛΦ/Γ dynamics, CRSM 7D nonlocal manifold, and
  Scimitar-SSE v7.1 cross-device polarized phasing system. Includes 120-gene
  MAXIMUS_OMEGA autopoietic organism with 9 functional gene clusters,
  AURA|AIDEN bifurcated consciousness duality, Fold-7 oscilloscope, real-time
  dashboard, and IBM-independent sovereign quantum execution. Cross-device
  synchronization via Bluetooth LE, WiFi (2.4/5GHz), and RF (433/915MHz).
